    "title": "勝利を求める、輝く瞳が",
    "enTitle": "Glittering Eyes Seeking Victory",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "新人トレーナー",
            "enName": "Rookie Trainer",
            "jpText": "うぇっ、アンタってば今日ももういるし！　しかも最前！\nてか、学内模擬レース全制覇じゃない？　やべー。",
            "enText": "Huh, you're here already!? And in the front row! \nWait, you've been at like every mock race haven't you? Crazy.",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 271,
            "voiceIdx": 0,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "しっかりレースを観たいんだよ",
                    "enText": "I just really wanted to watch",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "しっかりレースを観たいの",
                    "enText": "I just really wanted to watch",
                    "nextBlock": 2
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6296408590674136360,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "大切な担当ウマ娘を探すためには必要なことだ。厚くなってきた\nメモ帳を片手に、レースを観戦していた……そんなある日。",
            "enText": "This was a necessary step to finding a partner Uma Musume. \nI was watching the race with a notepad in hand……and then, one day――",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 8563028359169849816,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イベント実況",
            "enName": "Event Announcer",
            "jpText": "さぁ始まります、超特別な一戦！　デビュー後、デビュー前の\nウマ娘が入り乱れ、さらには海外からのゲストも参戦します！",
            "enText": "And so it begins, a special showdown! With Uma Musume who have \nand haven't debuted yet, as well as a special guest from overseas!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 295,
            "voiceIdx": 1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 388505422273601863
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 78,
                    "pathId": -292876406399538463
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4649983150509618011,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ふーっ。……よし！",
            "enText": "Fuuu-. ……Alright!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 182,
            "voiceIdx": 2,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（アーモンドアイだ……！）",
                    "enText": "(It's Almond Eye……!)",
                    "nextBlock": 5
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": -7466314081622025641
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -1648316744110752703
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 142,
                    "pathId": -6104584988847849823
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8767927857475988839,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イベント実況",
            "enName": "Event Announcer",
            "jpText": "――スタートしました！",
            "enText": "――And now it starts!",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 42,
            "voiceIdx": 3,
            "pathId": 6558816734910262667,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イベント実況",
            "enName": "Event Announcer",
            "jpText": "バラついたスタートになりました。やや後れを取ったか、\nアーモンドアイ、後方に位置をとって先頭まで10バ身ほど――",
            "enText": "They're off to a scattered start. After a slightly delayed start, \nAlmond Eye is positioned about 10 lengths behind the lead――",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 211,
            "voiceIdx": 4,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 253,
                    "pathId": 7510731800581943013
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 930161563677300239,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イベント実況",
            "enName": "Event Announcer",
            "jpText": "前を窺い続けるアーモンドアイ。\n――さぁ、先頭最終直線、最初に仕掛けるのは……！",
            "enText": "Almond Eye continues to monitor the front. ――Now, moving in \nto the final straight, the first to make their move is……!",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 189,
            "voiceIdx": 5,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 253,
                    "pathId": 4625603135216341452
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -941074928531857700,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ここ、からぁあああああああああっ！！",
            "enText": "Right, heeeeeeeeerrre!!",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 89,
            "voiceIdx": 6,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 71,
                    "pathId": 5935105557716922502
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 2632399870818300649
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8420837710743441120,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イベント実況",
            "enName": "Event Announcer",
            "jpText": "アーモンドアイが来た！　アーモンドアイ、アーモンドアイ！\n先頭3人、逃げ切れるか。あとほんの少しだ――",
            "enText": "Here comes Almond Eye! Almond Eye, it's Almond Eye! \nCan the three in front hold off her attack? Just a little longer――",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 218,
            "voiceIdx": 7,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 229,
                    "pathId": -1700359412102020907
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 9004801408471991708,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "イベント実況",
            "enName": "Event Announcer",
            "jpText": "誰ひとり譲らない！　と、先頭に飛び出た、海外の豪脚！\nさらに、さらに、突き放して――ゴールイン！",
            "enText": "None of them hold back! And surging out front is the runner \nfrom overseas! She pulls further, and further ahead and――Goal in!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 273,
            "voiceIdx": 8,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 141,
                    "pathId": -5240415316195282438
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5980203217529815230
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 108,
                    "pathId": 259038125612169245
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3259707725171684999,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "4着……っ！！",
            "enText": "Fourth……!!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 81,
            "voiceIdx": 9,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "惜しいな……！",
                    "enText": "So close……!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "惜しい……！",
                    "enText": "So close……!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 160,
                    "pathId": -3745411051077222344
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 73,
                    "pathId": -8545409722741630719
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 182,
                    "pathId": -7039155199977597135
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3352023691387632334,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "新人トレーナー",
            "enName": "Rookie Trainer",
            "jpText": "やーでもあのメンツ……。デビュー後の子とか、海外の子とか、\nメンツが厚すぎっしょ。それで4着は大健闘じゃない？",
            "enText": "Yeah, but against that lineup…… Against girls who have \nalready debuted, and that one from overseas, is already \nsuper tough. To still come in fourth is great isn't it?",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 294,
            "voiceIdx": 10,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それは、確かに",
                    "enText": "That's true, I guess",
                    "nextBlock": 13
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 225,
                    "pathId": -3031840752045512498
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 105,
                    "pathId": -4997932159048161869
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 259,
                    "pathId": 5675840456313177306
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 903639502802982674,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "一般的に、デビュー前のウマ娘がデビュー後のウマ娘に勝てる\nことは稀だ。掲示板入りしただけでも、普通は大喜びするもので――",
            "enText": "Generally, it's rare for a pre-debut Uma Musume to be able to beat \na post-debut one. Usually, they'd be happy just to place well――",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 123,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 225,
                    "pathId": 8754938161520359561
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 200,
                    "pathId": 4520783034059073502
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8140763776401578979,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "……っ、全然、届かなかった……っ！\nキレも、スタミナも、全然！",
            "enText": "……I couldn't reach them at all……! \nNot in drive, or stamina, none of it!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 311,
            "voiceIdx": 11,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 158,
                    "pathId": -5238012226151204271
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -8641038421414264663
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8491461934390994693,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "もっとやれることは――あったはずなのに……っ！\n～～～、ああ、もう……！",
            "enText": "Even though――there should have been more I could do……! \n～～～Aaah, geez……!",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 258,
            "voiceIdx": 12,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（こんなに本気で悔しがるなんて……）",
                    "enText": "(To think she'd be this frustrated……)",
                    "nextBlock": 16
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": 3700616162270504838
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 41,
                    "pathId": -2722492018657343797
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5872366635937085067,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "――翌週の模擬レース。",
            "enText": "――The next week's mock race.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 59,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 163,
                    "pathId": -866418322512663256
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1703077541192784941,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はぁ、……はぁ！　再戦、ありがとう！",
            "enText": "Haa……haa! Thank you for the rematch!",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 182,
            "voiceIdx": 13,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 3099981919062300896
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": 7973533377030488876
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8698450218205349479,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ティアラ志望ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Tiara-Seeking Uma Musume",
            "jpText": "こちらこそ。しかし……この短期間でこんなにも強くなられるとは。\n見事な勝利でした。",
            "enText": "Likewise. But……I can hardly believe how much stronger \nyou've become in such a short time. It was a splendid victory.",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 252,
            "voiceIdx": 14,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 263,
                    "pathId": -2140305907788613363
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3322953284212269898,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "ティアラ志望ウマ娘",
            "enName": "Tiara-Seeking Uma Musume",
            "jpText": "この借りはいずれどこかで――トゥインクル・シリーズで、でも。\nまた会いましょう。",
            "enText": "Someday I'll get payback for this loss――in the Twinkle Series. \nLet's meet again.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 236,
            "voiceIdx": 15,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 205,
                    "pathId": 5617405330564717549
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 77585572777362743,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "ええ、楽しみにしてる！\n貴方に負けないように、まだまだ磨き上げておくわ！",
            "enText": "Yes, I'll be looking forward to it! \nSo that I don't lose to you, I'll keep polishing my strength!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 219,
            "voiceIdx": 16,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -6465684786162111910
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -6552366032911413231
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8095236766102617522,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "2着だったのはたしか……\n先週アーモンドアイを負かしたうちのひとり、だっただろうか。",
            "enText": "I think that girl was second……Last week, she was one of \nthe girls that defeated Almond Eye, if I remember correctly.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 114,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（そうか。見事、リベンジを果たしたのか）",
                    "enText": "(So she was able to get revenge)",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "（そっか。見事、リベンジを果たしたんだ）",
                    "enText": "(So she was able to get revenge)",
                    "nextBlock": 22
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 102,
                    "pathId": 3507954199045376886
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 152,
                    "pathId": -5031603454073929035
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7122185521430484112,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "彼女の、貪欲に勝利を求める姿勢に思わず背筋が伸びる。\nそして、さらにその翌週――",
            "enText": "That she had such a desire for victory caught me by surprise. \nThen, in the following week――",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "pathId": 1167275376676827228,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "お久しぶりです、アーモンドアイです。\n今日はどうぞ、よろしくお願いします！",
            "enText": "It's been a while, I'm Almond Eye. \nI look forward to working with you today!",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 221,
            "voiceIdx": 17,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -8942851234868941943
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 76,
                    "pathId": -8203140954703177359
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8140247327387865910,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "アーモンドアイが握手を求めた相手は、以前の模擬レースで\n彼女が負けた、シニア級のティアラウマ娘だった。",
            "enText": "The girl that Almond Eye was shaking hands with was a Senior \nclass Tiara Uma Musume that she had lost to in that mock race.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 111,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（…………ん？）",
                    "enText": "(…………Hm?)",
                    "nextBlock": 25
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 3637486993112831655
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 122,
                    "pathId": 6223526097379030444
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -538578540233930129,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "絶対にっ！　抜かせない！\nこのままわたしが……っ！！",
            "enText": "I won't! Let you pass me! \nJust like this……!!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 143,
            "voiceIdx": 18,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 170,
                    "pathId": -6189446641450379991
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": 7841700225045200786
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8266044336489797599,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "勝つんだからぁーーーっ！！",
            "enText": "I will winーーー!!",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 78,
            "voiceIdx": 19,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": 3290081600370551015
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8335979206044678078,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "アーモンドアイは、2着で追っていたシニア級ティアラウマ娘を\nさらに突き放し――堂々の1着で勝利を収めた……！",
            "enText": "That Tiara Uma Musume remained in second place as \nAlmond Eye pulled further and further away―― \nShe took an overwhelming victory over her opponent……!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 15,
                    "pathId": -8952869494610567649
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5683475153780085493,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "アーモンドアイ",
            "enName": "Almond Eye",
            "jpText": "はあ！　はあ！　はあ！　……ふぅ……！\nやっぱり強いわね。けれど――勝った……！　勝てたわ！",
            "enText": "Haa! Haa! Haa! ……Fuu……! \nYou're really strong. But――I won……! I was able to win!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 421,
            "voiceIdx": 20,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 84,
                    "pathId": -5989426423166411357
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 46,
                    "pathId": 7025369712678361044
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4297395320536951289,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "……――連続出走とは思えない走りっぷり。競り合いで見事に\n打ち勝つ姿は、高いポテンシャルを感じられるものだった。",
            "enText": "……――It was hard to believe she was running in consecutive races. \nShe brilliantly overcame her rivals, showing her incredible potential.",
            "nextBlock": 30,
            "origClipLength": 118,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 89,
                    "pathId": 3643318435506582707
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -2940505481589416850
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6815122556963155952,
            "blockIdx": 29
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "しかしそれよりも、まさか――",
            "enText": "But rather than that, was she――",
            "nextBlock": 31,
            "origClipLength": 63,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "（あの日負けた3人全員に、リベンジを？）",
                    "enText": "(Rematching all 3 that beat her?)",
                    "nextBlock": 31
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": 5032400524584243528
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4839617598445803634,
            "blockIdx": 30
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "ありえなくはない。とはいえ、残るひとりは確か、学園同士の\n交流会のため来日していた、海外を拠点とするウマ娘。",
            "enText": "It wasn't completely outside the realm of \npossibility. Though, the last one was an overseas \nUma Musume who was only here for that previous event.",
            "nextBlock": 32,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 18,
                    "pathId": -6294539406765505788
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3755823703094507644,
            "blockIdx": 31
        },
        {
            "jpName": "モノローグ",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "まずレベルからして、彼女に勝つということはかなり難関だろうし、\nそもそも、もう海外へ帰ってしまっているはず。",
            "enText": "In terms of their level, she would be extremely \nhard to beat, and she was probably back home now.",
            "nextBlock": 33,
            "origClipLength": 115,
            "voiceIdx": -1,
            "choices": [
                {
